ygData.msgSnippet: Solo?  Well then, you need to hit the hermit in SK.  He ll still give you good exp and money until you hit 28th.  At this point, I have been hunting the new
ygData.messageBody:
Solo? Well then, you need to hit the hermit in SK. He'll still give you
good exp and money until you hit 28th. At this point, I have been hunting
the new icy orcs in Everfrost with a ranger buddy of mine. Once I hit 31 or
32, it's time for one-eyes and HGs :o)

-=B=-
28th on Rathe
(28 is a hell level for solo'rs)
